import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Box, Grid, Card, CardContent, CardMedia, Button } from '@mui/material';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

const Trainers = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  return (
    <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: '#f5f5f5', minHeight: '100vh', pt: 4, pb: 6 }}>
      <Container>
        <Box
          sx={{
            backgroundColor: '#000000',
            padding: 4,
            borderRadius: 2,
            marginBottom: 4,
          }}
        >
          <Typography
            variant="h2"
            component="h1"
            gutterBottom
            sx={{
              color: '#FFFFFF',
              textAlign: 'center',
              fontWeight: 'bold',
              textTransform: 'uppercase',
            }}
          >
            Our Elite Trainers
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="h5"
            sx={{
              color: '#FFFFFF',
              textAlign: 'center',
              mb: 4,
            }}
          >
            Transform your life with Africa's finest fitness experts
          </Typography>
        </Box>

        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="300"
                image="/images/trainer1.jpg"
                alt="Coach Alain"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2" sx={{ color: '#000000' }}>
                  Coach Alain Kakoba
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ color: '#666666', mb: 2 }}>
                  Elite strength coach with 10+ years experience in powerlifting and functional training. Specializes in building lean muscle and improving athletic performance.
                </Typography>
                <Button
                  variant="contained"
                  fullWidth
                  onClick={() => navigate('/booking')}
                  sx={{
                    backgroundColor: '#FF0000',
                    '&:hover': {
                      backgroundColor: '#CC0000',
                    },
                  }}
                >
                  Book Session
                </Button>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="300"
                image="/images/trainer2.jpg"
                alt="Coach Amara"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2" sx={{ color: '#000000' }}>
                  Coach Amara Diallo
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ color: '#666666', mb: 2 }}>
                  Certified HIIT specialist and former professional athlete. Expert in weight loss transformation and high-intensity cardio programs. Passionate about helping clients achieve their fitness goals.
                </Typography>
                <Button
                  variant="contained"
                  fullWidth
                  onClick={() => navigate('/booking')}
                  sx={{
                    backgroundColor: '#FF0000',
                    '&:hover': {
                      backgroundColor: '#CC0000',
                    },
                  }}
                >
                  Book Session
                </Button>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="300"
                image="/images/trainer3.jpg"
                alt="Coach Chioma"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2" sx={{ color: '#000000' }}>
                  Coach Chioma Okafor
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ color: '#666666', mb: 2 }}>
                  Holistic wellness expert with expertise in nutrition and body transformation. Specializes in creating personalized meal plans and lifestyle coaching for sustainable results.
                </Typography>
                <Button
                  variant="contained"
                  fullWidth
                  onClick={() => navigate('/booking')}
                  sx={{
                    backgroundColor: '#FF0000',
                    '&:hover': {
                      backgroundColor: '#CC0000',
                    },
                  }}
                >
                  Book Session
                </Button>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Trainers;
